ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under Sections 160, 191 and 209 of the Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999 and Repealing the List of Hazardous Waste Authorities (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending certain REGULATIONS MADE UNDER SECTIONS 160, 191 AND 209 OF THE CANADIAN ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION ACT, 1999 AND REPEALING THE LIST OF HAZARDOUS WASTE AUTHORITIES (Miscellaneous Program) in order improve the clarity and consistency of the regulatory texts, align the English and French versions of each of the Regulations, and repeal the List.
